### News API root
### https://localhost:7773/api/v1/news
###

### Search API - no filters
### Expected: returns a validation message because at least one search parameter is required.
GET https://localhost:7773/api/v1/news/search

###

### Search API - filter by category
GET https://localhost:7773/api/v1/news/search?category=Technology

###

### Search API - filter by language
GET https://localhost:7773/api/v1/news/search?language=EN

###

### Search API - filter by country
GET https://localhost:7773/api/v1/news/search?country=US

###

### Search API - combine language, country, and category filters
GET https://localhost:7773/api/v1/news/search?language=EN&country=US&category=Technology

###

### Search API - search by query text within a category
GET https://localhost:7773/api/v1/news/search?query=technology&category=Technology

###

### Search API - search by keyword
GET https://localhost:7773/api/v1/news/search?searchKeyWords=bitcoin

###

### Search API - apply paging and sort by publication date
GET https://localhost:7773/api/v1/news/search?language=EN&country=US&page=1&pageSize=5&sortBy=publishedAt

###

### Search API - search by title keyword
GET https://localhost:7773/api/v1/news/search?qInTitle=ai&language=EN&country=US

###

### Search API - filter by one or more domains
GET https://localhost:7773/api/v1/news/search?domains=techcrunch.com&domains=theverge.com&language=EN

###

### Search API - filter by one or more sources
GET https://localhost:7773/api/v1/news/search?sources=bbc-news&sources=the-verge&language=EN
